ur behalf.",url:"https://www.deel.com/payroll/contractor-of-record/"},{name:"Global Payroll",description:"Multi-country payroll processing with local compliance, tax filing, and consolidated reporting.",url:"https://www.deel.com/payroll/global/"},{name:"US Payroll",description:"Payroll for US-based employees across all 50 states with automated tax calculations and filings.",url:"https://www.deel.com/payroll/us/"},{name:"PEO",description:"Co-employment model for US companies that want outsourced HR, payroll, and benefits administration.",url:"https://www.deel.com/payroll/peo/"}]},{category:"HR",items:[{name:"HRIS",description:"Core HR system of record — employee profiles, onboarding workflows, PTO tracking, and reporting.",url:"https://www.deel.com/hr-platform/hris/"},{name:"Workforce Planning",description:"Headcount planning, scenario modeling, and approval workflows for HR and finance teams.",url:"https://www.deel.com/hr/workforce-planning/"},{name:"Compensation Management",description:"Global pay review cycles, benchmarking, and compensation band management.",url:"https://www.deel.com/hr/compensation-management/"},{name:"Employee Engagement",description:"Performance reviews, career development frameworks, learning management, and surveys.",url:"https://www.deel.com/hr/engage/"},{name:"Employee Benefits",description:"Benefits administration with carrier integrations and payroll deduction sync.",url:"https://www.deel.com/hr/employee-benefits-software/"},{name:"Employee Equity",description:"Stock option and equity plan administration in 110+ countries with local tax compliance.",url:"https://www.deel.com/hr-services/employee-equity/"},{name:"Background Checks",description:"Employment screening in 190+ countries, integrated directly into the onboarding workflow.",url:"https://www.deel.com/hr-services/employee-background-checks/"},{name:"Employee Immigration",description:"Visa and work permit processing for employee relocations across countries.",url:"https://www.deel.com/hr-services/employee-immigration/"}]},{category:"IT",items:[{name:"Device Lifecycle Management",description:"Procure, ship, manage, and recover devices for employees in any country.",url:"https://www.deel.com/it/device-lifecycle-management/"},{name:"Mobile Device Management",description:"Remote device configuration, updates, and security policies across operating systems.",url:"https://www.deel.com/it/mobile-device-management/"},{name:"Endpoint Protection",description:"Threat monitoring and device security for distributed workforces.",url:"https://www.deel.com/it/endpoint-protection/"},{name:"Identity & Access Management",description:"Automated app provisioning and de-provisioning tied to HR events.",url:"https://www.deel.com/it/identity-access-management/"}]},{category:"Platform",items:[{name:"Deel AI",description:"AI assistant trained on Deel compliance and HR data across 150+ countries.",url:"https://www.deel.com/hr-platform/ai/"},{name:"Compliance",description:"Automated contract generation, tax form collection, and local labor law compliance.",url:"https://www.deel.com/hr-platform/compliance/"},{name:"Integrations",description:"Pre-built connectors for HRIS, accounting, ATS, and collaboration tools.",url:"https://www.deel.com/integrations/"},{name:"API",description:"REST API for syncing employee, payroll, and contractor data with external systems.",url:"https://www.deel.com/hr-platform/api/"},{name:"White Label",description:"Embed Deel's payroll and HR infrastructure under your own brand.",url:"https://www.deel.com/hr-platform/white-label/"}]}],o=[{name:"deel_get_products",description:"Returns the full catalogue of Deel products grouped by category (Hiring & Payroll, HR, IT, Platform). Each product includes a name, description, and a link to its marketing page on deel.com. Use this when a user asks what Deel offers, which products are available, or wants to compare product areas.",inputSchema:{type:"object",properties:{}},annotations:{title:"Get Deel Produc